Class YoutubeExtraction

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.pulsebeat02.minecraftmedialibrary.extractor.YoutubeExtraction
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    VideoExtractorBase

    public class YoutubeExtraction
extends java.lang.Object
implements VideoExtractorBase
    Youtube extraction class used to extract audio from video files. Very useful for extraction media from a specific link.
